### Tooltip

Use the `title` prop to wrap the button in a tooltip. This is useful for icon-only buttons or whenever additional context helps the user understand the action.

<Example demo="button-title-demo">
  <ButtonTitleDemo />
</Example>

### Link as Button

Use `LinkButton` when the interaction should navigate somewhere but still look like a button. Use `Button` for in-place actions like submitting, opening, or toggling UI.

<Example demo="button-as-link-demo">
  <ButtonAsLinkDemo />
</Example>

## API Reference

### Button

Renders a native button with Kumo variants and optional tooltip wrapping.

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `variant` | `"primary" \| "secondary" \| "ghost" \| "destructive" \| "secondary-destructive" \| "outline"` | No | Visual style. Defaults to `"secondary"`. |
| `size` | `"xs" \| "sm" \| "base" \| "lg"` | No | Button size. Defaults to `"base"`. |
| `shape` | `"base" \| "square" \| "circle"` | No | Button shape. Use compact shapes for icon-only actions. |
| `icon` | `Component` | No | Svelte component rendered before the label. |
| `loading` | `boolean` | No | Shows a loader and disables the button while true. |
| `title` | `Snippet \| string` | No | Wraps the button in a tooltip with the given content. |
| `disabled` | `boolean` | No | Disables the button. |
| `children` | `Snippet` | No | Button label or custom child markup. |

All other props are passed to the underlying `<button>` element. The default `type` is `"button"`.

### LinkButton

Renders an anchor styled like a Kumo button for navigation actions.

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `href` | `string` | No | Link destination. |
| `variant` | `"primary" \| "secondary" \| "ghost" \| "destructive" \| "secondary-destructive" \| "outline"` | No | Visual style. Defaults to `"ghost"`. |
| `size` | `"xs" \| "sm" \| "base" \| "lg"` | No | Button size. Defaults to `"base"`. |
| `shape` | `"base" \| "square" \| "circle"` | No | Link button shape. |
| `icon` | `Component` | No | Svelte component rendered before the label. |
| `external` | `boolean` | No | Opens the link in a new tab with `rel="noopener noreferrer"`. |
| `children` | `Snippet` | No | Link label or custom child markup. |

All other props are passed to the underlying `<a>` element.
